Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.25,0:00:18.22,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,What is this thing we call emotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:21.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Can it be brought into the light?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.75,0:00:25.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Where is it now? Is it on vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:29.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Can someone help me out of my mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So many memories are jumbled and twisted
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:36.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Crossed out the faces, and let go of friends
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:40.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The line is slender between death and sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.46,0:00:44.23,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I've~ seen it over and over again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.25,0:00:48.22,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,No more to this one, and no more to that one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:51.73,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Some thoughts are smeared~ with a canvas of black
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.71,0:00:55.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'm~ not ashamed~ of the pieces I'm missing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.50,0:00:59.54,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,They're not much to~ la-a-a-a-ack
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.25,0:01:01.93,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The shadow clouds our sight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:03.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But we know that, to light,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:06.81,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The dark will surren~der
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:09.39,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So let us not forget
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.62,0:01:11.26,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Of all the good we met
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:14.97,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We~ will~ remember
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:03.29,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Wonderful times or painful reflections
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:06.73,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Confusing thoughts are plain as can be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:10.79,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It's all a maze of endless directions
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:14.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But who said happiness would be free?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:18.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I feel afraid, of all the memories ma-ade
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.00,0:02:22.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And how~ they'll~ remind~ me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.79,0:02:26.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But I guess that's okay, 'cause I know that one day~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:29.86,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You'll come~ ba-ack to fi-ind me~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:36.22,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And once aga-a-ain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:43.37,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Oooh, I lose~ a frie-e-e-end
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:47.63,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The faces come and go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:52.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,They take a toll on~ knowing how~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:55.44,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,They'll all be gone one day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:02:59.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Yet nothin' seems~ to slow me down~
